OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FITV News reporter Elaine Wilcox spoke
OL,8,Fto Manchester Central Mosque
OL,9,Fworshipper Maryam, who did not want to
OL,10,Fshow her face
OL,12,FA worshipper at Manchester Central
OL,13,FMosque has criticised the decision to
OL,14,Fnot treat the incident as terror-
OL,15,Frelated after two men allegedly
OL,16,Fentered "carrying multiple weapons".
OL,18,FPolice were called following reports
OL,19,Fthat two "suspicious" men entered
OL,20,Fduring Ramadan prayers at around
OL,21,F8:40pm on Tuesday 24 February.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FOne man was arrested and remains in
OL,8,Fcustody, and a search is underway to
OL,9,Flocate a second man.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) said
OL,12,Fthe incident is not being treated as
OL,13,Fterror-related - but it is engaging
OL,14,Fwith Counter Terrorism Policing North
OL,15,FWest.
OL,17,FOfficers say the men had claimed to be
OL,18,Fin the Mosque to do work on the
OL,19,Fbuilding - which staff were unaware of.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FBut Maryam, a muslim woman who attends
OL,8,Fthe Mosque, says the incident falls
OL,9,Funder terrorism.
OL,11,F"I think the fact we're even having a
OL,12,Fconversation about whether it's a
OL,13,Fterror attack or not is ridiculous,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"The definition of terror is extreme
OL,8,Ffear, and what's more fearful then
OL,9,Fwhen you've got your kids with you,
OL,10,Fyou're in a place of worship, you're
OL,11,Fpraying- the most peaceful thing in
OL,12,Fthe world - and there's people coming
OL,13,Fin with deadly weapons."
OL,15,FMaryam said the decision not to treat
OL,16,Fis as such feels like a "betrayal".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FShe added: "I think as muslims we are
OL,8,Freally strong in our identity because
OL,9,Fwe are so used to - in this country -
OL,10,Ffeeling misunderstood and misheard and
OL,11,Fmisrepresented. It's just really sad
OL,12,Fto see the reaction to it."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Mosque said the
OL,15,Fmen were carrying bags, with one
OL,16,Fbelieved to be containing an axe and
OL,17,Fthe other a hammer and a knife.
OL,19,FGMP added nobody was injured and no
OL,20,Ffurther threats have been made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
