PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FMaryam said the muslim community is
OL,8,Fnow used to these threats happening
OL,9,F"again and again and again".
OL,11,FShe said: "There's always been
OL,12,Fviolence every year, there's always
OL,13,Fbeen threats and there's been worse
OL,14,Fthan this in the past few years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"I don't think there's a rise in
OL,8,Fattacks on the muslim community, I
OL,9,Fjust think we are continuously letting
OL,10,Fthings go and letting things be
OL,11,Fglossed over and not taking things
OL,12,Fseriously and it's creating further
OL,13,Fdivision."
OL,15,FMeanwhile the chairman of Manchester
OL,16,FCentral Mosque has asked for increased
OL,17,Fpolice presence after what the Prime
OL,18,FMinister has called the "concerning"
OL,19,Fincident.
OL,26,@zD@YOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FHammad Khan said the suspect was "very
OL,8,Fcalm" and had been spotted visiting
OL,9,Fthe mosque, in the Victoria Park area
OL,10,Fof south Manchester, before the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FHowever, after entering the mosque
OL,14,Faround 8.30pm, where around 1,500
OL,15,Fpeople were saying Ramadan prayers, an
OL,16,Faxe was spotted in his bag and he was
OL,17,Fushered into an office by volunteers
OL,18,Fand police called.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,FHe had a knife and a hammer on him,
OL,8,Falong with "other materials" relating
OL,9,Fto the Second World War and some
OL,10,Fnewspaper cuttings.
OL,12,FMr Khan added: "His demeanour was very
OL,13,Fcalm.
OL,15,F"He wasn't under the influence of
OL,16,Fanything at all. I also understand he
OL,17,Fwas also carrying some other materials
OL,18,Fwith him relating to World War Two,
OL,19,Falso some newspaper cuttings, which
OL,20,Fthe police have.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@\O]tD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"The volunteers obviously kept the
OL,8,Fconversation going in very amenable
OL,9,Fway to ensure the situation did not
OL,10,Fescalate in any way."
OL,12,FMr Khan said he had asked police for
OL,13,Fan increased police presence around
OL,14,Fall the local mosques after an
OL,15,Fincrease in hate mail and threats.
OL,17,FHe added: "I was disappointed that we
OL,18,Fdidn't have visible presence.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@UO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"I stressed prior to the month of
OL,8,FRamadan we needed police presence
OL,9,Fbecause prayers go on to late at
OL,10,Fnight."
OL,12,FManchester Central Mosque said in a
OL,13,Fstatement: "The Muslim community in
OL,14,Fthe UK has experienced a notable rise
OL,15,Fin threats and hostility over recent
OL,16,Fyears,
OL,18,F"The increase in Islamophobic
OL,19,Fincidents is a serious concern, and
OL,20,Fgreater resources are urgently needed
OL,21,Fto address this growing and real risk.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"Congregants are advised to travel in
OL,8,Fgroups where possible and to ensure
OL,9,Fthat children are not left unattended."
OL,11,FA statement from the Greater
OL,12,FManchester Combined Authority said:
OL,13,F"We know last night's incident at
OL,14,FManchester Central Mosque is a cause
OL,15,Fof deep concern for those present and
OL,16,Ffor our Muslim communities across the
OL,17,Fwhole city region, particularly during
OL,18,Fthe holy month of Ramadan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"It is important to say there were no
OL,8,Fdirect threats nor any violence used.
OL,9,FHowever, there is no complacency.
OL,10,FWhile we are relieved no one was hurt,
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police are treating
OL,12,Fthis as a serious incident and have an
OL,13,Fongoing investigation.
OL,15,F"We commend those at the mosque who
OL,16,Facted quickly to alert GMP and we will
OL,17,Fbe visiting later today to listen to
OL,18,Fmembers of the community and provide
OL,19,Fwhat reassurance we can.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"GMP has also given us an assurance
OL,8,Fthat there will be an increased police
OL,9,Fpresence at all of our mosques over
OL,10,Fthe coming hours, as part of ongoing
OL,11,Fwork to strengthen security around all
OL,12,Fplaces of worship in Greater
OL,13,FManchester."
OL,15,FLucy Powell, MP for Manchester Central
OL,16,Fand Deputy Leader of the Labour Party,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Very concerning incident at
OL,18,FManchester Central Mosque.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772093097
OL,3,C'How could it not be a terror
OL,4,Cattack?': Call for more police at
OL,5,CMosque
OL,7,F"Thanks to the vigilance of volunteers
OL,8,Fand the action of police a more
OL,9,Fserious incident was avoided. Those
OL,10,Fresponsible must face full force of
OL,11,Fthe law. We must root out Islamophobia
OL,12,Fand Muslim hate and all those who
OL,13,Fperpetrate it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
